{"tid":2364432,"cid":21,"subCid":2,"title":"覺唔覺啲人話周杰倫冇左方文山就唔掂其實好好笑","createTime":"2021-01-13T03:52:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-30T14:08:57.000Z","uid":1627,"like":34,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"601635f5f58ebf7343dae315e4bc40fb37d13b1a","tid":2364432,"uid":1627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T03:52:12.000Z","msg":"星晴<br />\n黑色幽默<br />\n安靜<br />\n半島鐵盒<br />\n晴天<br />\n藉口<br />\n黑色毛衣<br />\n最長的電影<br />\n彩虹<br />\n給我一首歌的時間<br />\n以上呢10首耳熟能詳既情歌全部都係周杰倫自己作詞，如果係任何一個歌手有呢10首都夠佢食一世老本<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲未計佢自己作詞既rap，梯田同稻香都入圍金曲獎最佳作詞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不如調返轉咁講，方文山離開左周杰倫仲有咩詞作大家係講得出名<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我諗最出名應該都係醉赤壁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n邊個成就邊個都未分得清<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9ee7a02db3e13999012746ad01dbe10edf5ea5f","tid":2364432,"uid":200974,"like":3,"dislike":30,"score":-27,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T03:59:00.000Z","msg":"你確定你上面果幾首係周杰倫最紅果幾首？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0568b68007296139d991960b99c8e891b7a299c","tid":2364432,"uid":190187,"like":14,"dislike":4,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T04:01:53.000Z","msg":"其實方文山啲詞好表面"},{"pid":"b469ef49d25f3ef82491b86737a646b8d20f0ecd","tid":2364432,"uid":1627,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"qu